title: Mp3 My Mp3 Recorder 3.0
description: Record internet radio, save to mp3 or wav.Record streaming audio from the internet, microphone or any other source for that matter, works directly with your system sound card sooooo... If you can HEAR IT...you can RECORD it! This program is meant to be extremely intuitive to use, with enough features to get the job done quickly and easily. Customizable colors, timer, on top mode and skinning is also included. You can also rip CD's, batch rename, create playlists, enable silence detection, record vinyl albums, scheduled recordings and more.
